This project is a Kotlin Multiplatform application.

Tech stack:

- Kotlin Multiplatform
- Compose Multiplatform
- MVVM architecture
- Koin dependency injection
- Ktor client
- Coroutines and Flow
- Clean Architecture

Always follow rule files located in:

.cursor/rules/

When generating new features, follow the feature architecture pattern.

Always generate:

DTO
Mapper
Repository
UseCase
ViewModel
Compose Screen
DI module

Prefer commonMain unless platform code is required.

Never generate Android-only code unless explicitly requested.

Never hardcode user-facing strings in UI or ViewModel code.
Use Compose Multiplatform string resources and follow the string resource rules in `.cursor/rules/string-resources.mdc`.
